# CODEOWNERS for unisupply
#
# GitHub uses this file to auto-request reviews on pull requests.
#
# IMPORTANT: CODEOWNERS reviews are only *enforced* when branch protection is
# configured to require them. Branch protection lands in a PR; until
# then this file is dormant — it will request reviewers but cannot block a
# merge. (See OpenSSF Scorecard "Branch-Protection" check.)
#
# Catch-all: every PR — including bot PRs (Dependabot/Renovate) — routes to
# the maintainers team for review.

* @unidoc/unidoc-devs

# CI, release, and security workflows — extra-careful review on anything
# that affects how releases are built, signed, or attested.
/.github/                       @unidoc/unidoc-devs

# The trust anchor for release signing. Any change here is a security-
# critical event; treat reviews accordingly.
/.github/allowed_signers        @unidoc/unidoc-devs

# Product specification — design changes need maintainer sign-off.
/spec/                          @unidoc/unidoc-devs
